      "description": "Known for already havingan eponymous sitcom, Drew went with his co-star Ryan's idea of adapting this show for US audiences and became host and executive producer ofWhose Lineuntil its initial cancellation. Achilles' Heel: It's not hard to get Drew to laugh, but itishard to make himstop. Acrofatic: He's generally the stockiest of the cast, yet can still be quite spry when performing in the games. Adipose Rex: Drew was the performers' and musicians' boss during his run. He even sometimes jokes about Ryan's place on his sitcom show whenever he makes a joke on him.Drew:I have the power to hire and fire. Big Fun: Was often the butt of jokes about his weight but took them in good humor and enjoyed taking part in the games.",
